extendedInfo.description: Merry Christmas!Best Quality Christmas Ring TonesThis app includes 12 fabulous **high-quality** Christmas ringtones and Christmas sounds.   It allows you to easily preview the Christmas ring tones and sounds and then install them on your phone as a ringtone, notification tone (e.g. for e-mail and SMS), and/or alarm tone ringerSimple 1-click installer gets your Christmas ring tones and notification tones working easy peasy.Please tell your friends about this so they can enjoy the season as much as you do.Aaaaahhh Christmas!  Who doesn't love the sounds of Christmas ring tones?Keywords: Christmas, holiday, holidays, deck the halls, jingle bells, joy to the world, santa, santa claus, angels, angles, elves, ringtone, ringtones, ringer, sounds, christmas, christ, mass, Christ, Jesus, jesus, birthday, winter, wintertime, winter time, ringtone installer, mom, moms, love, christmas, Christmas
